  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>clarifies that a creditor may not charge a prepayment penalty and removes the existing exception;<hr><ltbullet>clarifies that the debtor is not entitled to a third party rebate unless the creditor becomes entitled to a rebate result from the prepayment; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
